{"tid":1165791,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人好鐘意用「唔差」呢個形容詞","createTime":"2019-05-22T04:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T05:25:41.000Z","uid":12498,"like":6,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"599ce9c5bbd844a6352288df62e671183c2b7057","tid":1165791,"uid":12498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:33:42.000Z","msg":"發覺唔少香港人都鐘意用「唔差」呢個詞。Eg：做得好好就會話「做得唔差」，明明係靚女都要話「個樣唔差」，etc.<br />\n其實係咪打從心底裡唔抵得人好，但佢又做得太好，逼於無奈要用「唔差」嚟讚人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a31a67c8dcf77fc9e680260cda339272092d52","tid":1165791,"uid":38904,"like":40,"dislike":1,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:36:26.000Z","msg":"樓豬個 post 喺差嗰方面都唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5f1da80165c00f2024979a6385847c5cef4fcc","tid":1165791,"uid":4285,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:37:51.000Z","msg":"香港人不嬲讚人好似會少咗忽肉咁"},{"pid":"ce0b18fc6bfc968930dcf908252ce3487d7a12e8","tid":1165791,"uid":49853,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"Ok啦"},{"pid":"c4e1aa5c0faa898baa09bc25a16e653870e45756","tid":1165791,"uid":71657,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:39:29.000Z","msg":"而事實上仲有更好同進步空間<br />\n講唔差有咩問題？"},{"pid":"95c42639672b8cae1e0e720f4fd5122e45b1e1b4","tid":1165791,"uid":86686,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:40:25.000Z","msg":"唔一定係唔抵得, 可以係含蓄"},{"pid":"63a6c8f4666390e44670d42ad27420ddfb205c23","tid":1165791,"uid":75870,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:40:33.000Z","msg":"鬼佬都會講not bad 你又點理解"},{"pid":"99167e264b113421c44c7cfba40e12019a34a54e","tid":1165791,"uid":30272,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T04:42:14.000Z","msg":"not bad = very good"},{"pid":"0a95737f63f74f5eacf7baed7e73102a7c829a06","tid":1165791,"uid":39684,"like":9,"dislike":1,"sc